<i>let us know and we'll</i>
<i>release a statement.</i>

20:17.433 --> 20:19.550
Will do, Your Eminence.
Thank you.

20:19.552 --> 20:21.385
- <i> Not at all.</i>
- We'll be in touch.

20:23.723 --> 20:25.189
Done.

20:27.060 --> 20:30.361
Wait, which one did
you say was Hobart again?

20:30.363 --> 20:35.199
Uh, 3F.
Right there.

20:37.120 --> 20:40.321
Yeah, that one.

20:40.323 --> 20:42.373
- Now, there.
- Yeah.

