mean I'd have to quit the team.

20:52.252 --> 20:53.668
No, no, no, no.

20:53.670 --> 20:55.386
I'll make do
on Tuesday.

20:55.388 --> 20:57.255
All right.

20:57.257 --> 20:59.507
