and no ring on my finger.

21:28.504 --> 21:30.922
Ah, I'll win him over
like any other constituent.

21:30.924 --> 21:32.206
You'll see.

21:32.208 --> 21:34.625
<i>♪ now, some may want to die,</i>
<i>young man... ♪</i>

21:34.627 --> 21:37.628
You should come to bed.
Tomorrow's gonna be a long day.

21:40.633 --> 21:43.467
Tomorrow
is gonna be hell.

21:43.469 --> 21:48.389
<i>♪ hey, buddy,</i>
<i>that ain't me... ♪</i>

21:48.391 --> 21:51.392
<i>That's-- that's--</i>

21:51.394 --> 21:55.613
that's the only plan
that makes sense for the city.

21:55.615 --> 21:59.033
Thank you, Councilman.
Mr. Spallone?

21:59.035 --> 22:01.986
You know, I'm not like these
wimps who are kowtowing

22:01.988 --> 22:04.488
to some judge who's off
the friggin' wall.

22:06.242 --> 22:09.660
I'm not wearing Pampers.

22:09.662 --> 22:12.496
I swore an allegiance
to you, the voters,

22:12.498 --> 22:15.049
and I'm gonna keep that
allegiance to you,

22:15.051 --> 22:17.635
and I got a message
for Judge Sands.

22:17.637 --> 22:20.137
Nuts to Judge Sands.

22:20.139 --> 22:21.672
You wanna take me away?

22:21.674 --> 22:24.976
Come get me!

22:24.978 --> 22:28.095
Great, we're one wing nut
away from a riot.

22:28.097 --> 22:32.483
Tell me about it. They confiscated
four guns at the door.

22:32.485 --> 22:34.852
I wonder which one of these
bastards sent the bullets.

22:37.740 --> 22:42.493
Uh, we're here to take testimony
from the citizens of Yonkers...

22:44.364 --> 22:46.998
...regarding
the housing site plan.

22:48.534 --> 22:51.202
Those who have signed up
and wish to make a statement

22:51.204 --> 22:55.122
may proceed to the podium
in the proper order.

22:55.124 --> 22:58.459
What I'd like to know is whatever
happened to majority rule, huh?

22:58.461 --> 23:01.212
- Yeah!
- Isn't this still America?

23:01.214 --> 23:05.800
- Yeah!
<i>- A bunch of wimps is what you all are!</i>

23:05.802 --> 23:08.052
It's about these
public housing people

23:08.054 --> 23:12.056
<i>bringing drugs and crime</i>
<i>into our neighborhood</i>

23:12.058 --> 23:16.027
and ruining
our property values!

23:16.029 --> 23:18.229
- You promised us an appeal!
- Yes!

23:18.231 --> 23:20.147
You promised
you wouldn't settle!

23:20.149 --> 23:24.285
You have succeeded in raping
the voters of their city!

23:26.906 --> 23:29.573
You people campaigned
on this issue.

23:29.575 --> 23:32.710
I knocked on doors
for you, Nick Longo.

23:32.712 --> 23:37.298
<i>And you, Ed Fagan, you
said, "I will go to jail."</i>

23:37.300 --> 23:39.750
<i>You're not even</i>
<i>a man of your word.</i>

23:39.752 --> 23:41.085
<i>You know,</i>
<i>we're gonna find out.</i>

23:41.087 --> 23:44.255
We're gonna find out
what deal was done

23:44.257 --> 23:47.391
and I think you're gonna regret
the day you went into politics.

23:47.393 --> 23:52.063
So enjoy the next
two years on the council!

23:52.065 --> 23:54.765
They're your last
two years!

23:54.767 --> 23:55.900
<i>Shame on you!</i>

23:55.902 --> 23:57.518
<i>You should be ashamed</i>
<i>of yourselves!</i>

23:57.520 --> 23:59.437
I'd like to remind
the speakers

23:59.439 --> 24:01.439
to be respectful
of the people up here.

24:01.441 --> 24:05.276
<i>Where's our respect?
No more lies!</i>

24:05.278 --> 24:09.029
No more lies!
No more lies!

24:09.031 --> 24:12.116
<i>No more lies! No more lies!</i>

24:12.118 --> 24:14.335
<i>No more lies!</i>

