objections of Yonkers residents,

24:22.929 --> 24:26.464
<i>hundreds of whom turned out tonight
to register their displeasure.</i>

24:26.466 --> 24:28.432
They're really
gonna build them.

24:28.434 --> 24:32.219
Yeah, the paper said that the Loring
and Clark site is still on the list.

24:32.221 --> 24:34.021
