of blocks from us.

24:34.023 --> 24:37.525
I mean, these people.

24:37.527 --> 24:40.311
They don't live
the way we do.

24:40.313 --> 24:43.481
They don't want
what we want.

24:43.483 --> 24:46.233
And their
neighborhoods...

24:46.235 --> 24:48.152
Yeah, a mess.

24:48.154 --> 24:50.988
Buddy, that's the last damn
meeting I'm going to miss.

24:50.990 --> 24:53.824
You mark my words.

24:53.826 --> 24:57.411
