Mr. Clerk,
roll call this vote.

25:07.340 --> 25:09.640
Mayor Wasicsko?

25:09.642 --> 25:11.509
Yes.

25:11.511 --> 25:13.227
<i>Vice Mayor Spallone.</i>

25:13.229 --> 25:14.979
No.

25:14.981 --> 25:17.648
- <i> Majority Leader Cola?</i>
<i>- Yes.</i>

25:17.650 --> 25:21.569
- <i> Minority Leader Longo?</i>
- Yes.

25:21.571 --> 25:24.104
- <i> Council Member Fagan?</i>
