another $160,000 for last month,

26:45.655 --> 26:47.404
which means
we've already spent,

26:47.406 --> 26:49.323
what, $15 million
fighting this thing?

26:49.325 --> 26:52.159
Yeah, well, what's another
couple hundred thousand?

26:52.161 --> 26:53.944
Come on, Nick. When we
accepted the consent decree,

26:53.946 --> 26:56.196
we gave up
our right to appeal.

26:56.198 --> 26:59.116
You go to the Supreme Court now, you
piss off Judge Sand all over again.

26:59.118 --> 27:02.286
All right, so we don't appeal the
