to do shit right.

28:00.513 --> 28:03.347
No, you ain't gotta
call nobody.

28:03.349 --> 28:05.849
What, you don't think
I know how to be a daddy?

28:05.851 --> 28:09.236
Yo, as soon as this boy come
out, I'm going back to school.

28:09.238 --> 28:11.405
School? You?

28:11.407 --> 28:13.524
Yeah, me.

28:13.526 --> 28:15.993
Westchester CC.

28:15.995 --> 28:18.412
In the spring.

28:18.414 --> 28:21.699
I mean, I want
to quit now, but...

28:21.701 --> 28:25.169
I need the cash so I can
step back and do it right.

28:27.923 --> 28:29.840
