28:55.534 --> 28:57.151
I got the banana.

28:57.153 --> 28:59.119
Good boy.

29:00.740 --> 29:03.407
Well, he home now.

29:03.409 --> 29:05.576
And you, too.

29:05.578 --> 29:07.544
It's better for them
here, Javier,

29:07.546 --> 29:10.381
but I am killing myself.

29:10.383 --> 29:12.499
I'm working at the school
